                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>
                Welcome to Food Ordering, your go-to place for delicious and
                diverse cuisines! Our restaurant is committed to providing
                high-quality meals with the freshest ingredients. Explore our
                menu and order your favorite dishes online.
